# 内置资源

  • Cargo.toml

    [dependencies]
rust-embed = "~5.9.0"

  • 创建目录assets，并将内置资源放置于此

  • main.rs

    use crate::{Asset};

#[derive(RustEmbed)]
#[folder = "./assets"]
pub struct Asset;

fn main() {
  for file in Asset::iter() {
    println!("{}", file.as_ref());
  }
}

/// 写到文件
pub fn writeEmbedFile(filePath: &str, outFilePath: &PathBuf) -> Result<(), Box<dyn Error>> {
  let file = Asset::get(filePath).unwrap();
  File::create(outFilePath).unwrap().write(&file)?;
  Ok(())
}
